      "label": "ContentLengthConstraint",
      "kind": "Characteristic",
      "preferredName": "Content Length Constraint",
      "description": "For each line, the customer transmits one DE 7102 in the PCI segment. In order to ensure that the code is correct, the DE 7102 must not exceed 25 characters per line. If the customer transmits more char-acters per line, all characters that exceed the prescribed length are lost when the label is printed."
    },
